                        "content": "The home care nurse is preparing to visit a client with a diagnosis of trigeminal neuralgia (tic douloureux). When performing the assessment, the nurse would plan to ask the client which question to elicit the most specific information regarding this disorder?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nTrigeminal neuralgia is characterized by spasms of pain that start suddenly and last for seconds to minutes. The pain often is characterized as stabbing or as similar to an electric shock. It is accompanied by spasms of facial muscles that cause twitching of parts of the face or mouth, or closure of the eye. The remaining options do not elicit data specifically related to this disorder.",
                        "id": "1e611659717f4ed0ab744640562bbe2c",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "ac27403264c94a71a81eacea85959e7a",
                                "content": "Prevent stressful situations."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "a59b2ee56f084be58734067b65834624",
                                "content": "Avoid activities that may cause fatigue."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "8961de069ac248f28f486361583f4dcd",
                                "content": "Avoid contact with people with an infection."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "82a900dc60a54a4bb7fd78aaf73f6206",
                                "content": "Avoid activities that may cause pressure near the face."
                            }
                        ],
