                        "content": "The nurse is providing instructions to the client with trigeminal neuralgia regarding measures to take to prevent the episodes of pain. Which would the nurse instruct the client to do?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nThe pain that accompanies trigeminal neuralgia is triggered by stimulation of the trigeminal nerve. Symptoms can be triggered by pressure, such as from washing the face, brushing the teeth, shaving, eating, or drinking. Symptoms also can be triggered by stimulation by a draft or cold air. The remaining options are not associated with triggering episodes of pain.",
                        "id": "91baa85d42b74f1fa371f75bb1965195",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "e7fec403551346689178190e861c91f8",
                                "content": "Cocoa with honey and toast"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "528dfe54833240248ee170cb7bf47e4a",
                                "content": "Hot herbal tea with graham crackers"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "371118b7cd66433abe0da446e296bc8e",
                                "content": "Iced coffee and peanut butter and crackers"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "ed8bd41384144e62b0f6fd1ddef120d8",
                                "content": "Vanilla wafers and room-temperature water"
                            }
                        ],
